cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a method for sim-to-real robot learning and evaluates it on a task of manipulating objects.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper involves training encoders and reinforcement learning algorithms.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as one of the encoders consumes RGB images.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper involves developing policies for manipulating objects.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper involves controlling a robotic system to manipulate objects.
